---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | Freedom Capital"
  description="Freedom Capital has been looking after private clients for 25 years, offering bespoke local and international equity portfolios."
>
  <!-- Hero section with blue background -->
  <section class="pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-20 md:pb-16 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--blue-900);">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase text-slate-300">
        Our Story
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        25 YEARS OF LOOKING AFTER PRIVATE CLIENTS
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gentle gradient fade -->
  <section class="h-32 grad-soft"></section>

  <!-- Main content in elevated card -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl p-12 md:p-16 space-y-8 text-slate-700 text-xl leading-relaxed text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);">
        <p>
          Paul Davis and Brett Sievwright started Watermark Securities (Pty) Ltd in 1999 as a member
          of the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE).
        </p>

        <p>
          Both of us had worked for established stock brokers and we identified the need for personalised
          private JSE services â€“ rather than chasing high volume institutional business.
        </p>

        <p>
          The removal of exchange controls and the ability to invest internationally necessitated a
          change in licence requirements and so the move from Watermark to a more fully fledged, multi
          FSCA licenced Freedom Capital (Pty) Ltd (FC) took place in 2014.
        </p>

        <p>
          Freedom Capital prides itself on very high levels of service in the industry and our loyal
          client base is testament to this character.
        </p>

        <p>
          We will continue to offer clients bespoke local and international equity share portfolios in
          both compulsory and non-compulsory investment structures.
        </p>

        <p>
          We love interacting with clients on a personal level and are strong believers in simplifying
          their finances in order to make the future as clear as possible.
        </p>

        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          We look forward to the next 25 years!
        </p>

        <div class="pt-6">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn text-lg">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
